ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle

Class SlotStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle.SlotStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FeatureContainerStyle, PropertyMappable, StyleHolder, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class SlotStyle
extends java.lang.Object
implements StyleHolder, java.lang.Cloneable, FeatureContainerStyle
    Defines a class for the style information for a particular slot. A slot is a ring/tract around the backbone where features and such can be placed into.
    Author:
    Aaron Petkau
